*** libXplane-UDP-Client ***

WHAT IS IT?

This is a C++ shared library for accessing X-Plane (http://www.x-plane.com) 
datarefs and commands over a network.


INSTALLING BINARIES

Binaries are available for Ubuntu 16.04 LTS (for x86_64) and Raspbian Stretch 
(for Raspberry Pi). To install the binaries, do the following:

- Install the repository public key:
	- From the repository itself:
	  wget -O- http://repo.shahada.abubakar.net/pubkey.asc | sudo apt-key add -
  - From ubuntu's key server:
	  gpg --keyserver keyserver.ubuntu.com --recv-key 2C4B99AE
		gpg --export --armor 2C4B99AE | sudo apt-key add -

- Add the APT source:
	sudo add-apt-repository "deb [arch=amd64] http://repo.shahada.abubakar.net/ stable main"
	sudo apt-get update

- Install the binaries:
  sudo apt-get install lib

